spec_data.Name: python2-py
spec_data.Description:
The py lib is a Python development support library featuring the
following tools and modules:

  * py.path: uniform local and svn path objects
  * py.apipkg: explicit API control and lazy-importing
  * py.iniconfig: easy parsing of .ini files
  * py.code: dynamic code generation and introspection
  * py.path: uniform local and svn path objects
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 17 Aug 2017 08:07:12 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Library with cross-python path, ini-parsing, io, code, log facilities
